reviews.review_text: A band in decline? You can comment on the recording dude, but the only thing in decline is your opinion. Stick to shows you actually went to maybe. Why even stop to rate it? You obviously don't get it whatsoever. Was my last show, was pregnant with my first child, miracled a girl in the lot, and will carry the music and snapshots in my mind till the end. Not fade away!
